{
  "name": "Backend Bootcamp — Registration Form (No Backend Required)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔐 SECTION 1 — Google OAuth Pre-Auth\n\nThis section handles Google sign-in **before** the registration form is shown.\n\n**Flow:**\n1. User visits `/webhook/bootcamp/auth/start`\n2. Redirected to Google consent screen\n3. Google returns to `/webhook/bootcamp/auth/callback?code=...`\n4. n8n exchanges code → gets user profile → registers session in backend\n5. Backend returns a signed `sessionToken`\n6. User is redirected to `/form/bootcamp-registration?token=<sessionToken>`\n\n**Required env variables:**\n- `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID`\n- `GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET`\n- `BACKEND_URL`\n- `N8N_BASE_URL`",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 480,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "00000001-0000-4000-8000-000000000001",
      "name": "Note — Google OAuth Flow",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-80, -600]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ⚙️ Required Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID` | Google OAuth App Client ID |\n| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET` | Google OAuth App Client Secret |\n| `BACKEND_URL` | Express.js backend base URL |\n| `N8N_BASE_URL` | Your n8n instance public URL |\n| `TELEGRAM_LIVE_GROUP_LINK` | Invite link for live class Telegram group |\n| `TELEGRAM_VIDEO_GROUP_LINK` | Invite link for video course Telegram group |\n| `QR_LIVE_CLASS_URL` | Hosted image URL for live class payment QR |\n| `QR_VIDEO_COURSE_URL` | Hosted image URL for video course payment QR |\n\n⚠️ Replace all placeholder values before activating this workflow.",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 460,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "00000001-0000-4000-8000-000000000002",
      "name": "Note — Environment Variables",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [420, -600]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📋 SECTION 2 — Registration Form (5 Pages)\n\n| Page | Content |\n|---|---|\n| 1 | Google token + Course selection |\n| 2 | Full name (English + Khmer) |\n| 3 | Academic background |\n| 4 | GitHub, expectations, referral |\n| 5 | Payment QR + screenshot upload |\n| 6 | Confirmation + Telegram group link |",
        "height": 220,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "00000001-0000-4000-8000-000000000003",
      "name": "Note — Form Pages",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [0, 440]
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "GET",
        "path": "bootcamp/auth/start",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "aa000001-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
      "name": "Google Auth — Start",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [0, -380],
      "webhookId": "b1a10001-c2d3-4e5f-6789-abcdef012345"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "respondWith": "redirect",
        "redirectURL": "=https://accounts.google.com/o/oauth2/v2/auth?client_id={{ $env.GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID }}&redirect_uri={{ encodeURIComponent($env.N8N_BASE_URL + '/webhook/bootcamp/auth/callback') }}&response_type=code&scope=openid%20email%20profile&access_type=offline&prompt=select_account",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "aa000002-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-aaaaaaaaaaab",
      "name": "→ Redirect to Google OAuth",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [260, -380]
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "GET",
        "path": "bootcamp/auth/callback",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "aa000003-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-aaaaaaaaaaac",
      "name": "Google Auth — Callback",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [0, -180],
      "webhookId": "b1a10002-c2d3-4e5f-6789-abcdef012346"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://oauth2.googleapis.com/token",
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "form-urlencoded",
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "code", "value": "={{ $json.query.code }}" },
            { "name": "client_id", "value": "={{ $env.GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID }}" },
            {
              "name": "client_secret",
              "value": "={{ $env.GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "redirect_uri",
              "value": "={{ $env.N8N_BASE_URL }}/webhook/bootcamp/auth/callback"
            },
            { "name": "grant_type", "value": "authorization_code" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "aa000004-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-aaaaaaaaaaad",
      "name": "Exchange Code for Token",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [280, -180]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "https://www.googleapis.com/oauth2/v2/userinfo",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Authorization",
              "value": "=Bearer {{ $json.access_token }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "aa000005-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-aaaaaaaaaaae",
      "name": "Get Google User Profile",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [560, -180]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "={{ $env.BACKEND_URL }}/api/auth/google/session",
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={{ JSON.stringify({ googleId: $json.id, email: $json.email, name: $json.name, picture: $json.picture }) }}",
        "options": {
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "neverError": true
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "aa000006-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-aaaaaaaaaaaf",
      "name": "Register Session in Backend",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [840, -180]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "respondWith": "redirect",
        "redirectURL": "={{ $env.N8N_BASE_URL }}/form/bootcamp-registration?token={{ encodeURIComponent($json.sessionToken) }}&gname={{ encodeURIComponent($('Get Google User Profile').item.json.name) }}&gemail={{ encodeURIComponent($('Get Google User Profile').item.json.email) }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "aa000007-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-aaaaaaaaaaag",
      "name": "→ Redirect to Registration Form",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [1120, -180]
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "formTitle": "🎓 Backend Development Bootcamp — Registration",
        "formDescription": "<div style='background:#eff6ff;border:1px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:10px;padding:18px 20px;margin-bottom:20px'>\n  <p style='margin:0 0 10px;font-weight:600;color:#1e40af;font-size:15px'>🔐 Step 1: Sign in with Google</p>\n  <p style='margin:0 0 14px;color:#3b5a9a;font-size:13px'>To prevent duplicate registrations, you must authenticate with your Google account first. A session token will be sent to your email after sign-in.</p>\n  <a href='/webhook/bootcamp/auth/start' target='_blank' style='display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:11px 20px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #dadce0;border-radius:6px;color:#3c4043;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.12)'>\n    <svg width='18' height='18' viewBox='0 0 48 48'><path fill='#EA4335' d='M24 9.5c3.54 0 6.71 1.22 9.21 3.6l6.85-6.85C35.9 2.38 30.47 0 24 0 14.62 0 6.51 5.38 2.56 13.22l7.98 6.19C12.43 13.72 17.74 9.5 24 9.5z'/><path fill='#4285F4' d='M46.98 24.55c0-1.57-.15-3.09-.38-4.55H24v9.02h12.94c-.58 2.96-2.26 5.48-4.78 7.18l7.73 6c4.51-4.18 7.09-10.36 7.09-17.65z'/><path fill='#FBBC05' d='M10.53 28.59c-.48-1.45-.76-2.99-.76-4.59s.27-3.14.76-4.59l-7.98-6.19C.92 16.46 0 20.12 0 24c0 3.88.92 7.54 2.56 10.78l7.97-6.19z'/><path fill='#34A853' d='M24 48c6.48 0 11.93-2.13 15.89-5.81l-7.73-6c-2.18 1.48-4.97 2.3-8.16 2.3-6.26 0-11.57-4.22-13.47-9.91l-7.98 6.19C6.51 42.62 14.62 48 24 48z'/></svg>\n    Continue with Google\n  </a>\n  <p style='margin:12px 0 0;color:#64748b;font-size:12px'>After signing in, copy the session token from the redirect page and paste it below.</p>\n</div>\n<p style='color:#475569;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 4px'>📌 Select the track that fits your learning style:</p>",
        "path": "bootcamp-registration",
        "responseMode": "lastNode",
        "formFields": {
          "values": [
            {
              "fieldLabel": "Google Session Token",
              "fieldType": "text",
              "requiredField": true,
              "placeholder": "Paste your session token here (obtained after Google sign-in above)"
            },
            {
              "fieldLabel": "Select Your Learning Track",
              "fieldType": "dropdown",
              "requiredField": true,
              "fieldOptions": {
                "values": [
                  {
                    "option": "🎬 Self-Paced Video Course — $29.99 (Lifetime access, learn at your own pace, new content added regularly)"
                  },
                  {
                    "option": "🎓 Live Online Class — $49.99 (Instructor-led, real-time Q&A, starts July 15 2026 · Tue & Thu 7–9 PM PNH)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "formTitle": "Step 1 of 5 — Choose Your Track",
          "buttonLabel": "Continue →"
        }
      },
      "id": "bb000001-bbbb-4bbb-8bbb-bbbbbbbbbb01",
      "name": "Form — Page 1: Auth + Course Selection",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.formTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [0, 200],
      "webhookId": "cc000001-dddd-4eee-8fff-000000000001"
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "={{ $env.BACKEND_URL }}/api/auth/verify-session",
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={{ JSON.stringify({ token: $json['Google Session Token'] }) }}",
        "options": {
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "neverError": true
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "bb000002-bbbb-4bbb-8bbb-bbbbbbbbbb02",
      "name": "Verify Auth Token",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [280, 200]
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "token-valid-check",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.valid }}",
              "rightValue": true,
              "operator": { "type": "boolean", "operation": "equals" }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "bb000003-bbbb-4bbb-8bbb-bbbbbbbbbb03",
      "name": "Auth Token Valid?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [560, 200]
    },

    {
      "parameters": {
        "formTitle": "⚠️ Authentication Failed",
        "formDescription": "<div style='text-align:center;padding:32px 20px'><div style='font-size:52px;margin-bottom:16px'>🔒</div><h2 style='color:#dc2626;margin:0 0 12px;font-size:20px'>Session Expired or Invalid</h2><p style='color:#64748b;margin:0 0 24px;font-size:14px'>Your Google session token is invalid, expired, or already used.<br/>Please sign in again to get a fresh token.</p><a href='/webhook/bootcamp/auth/start' style='display:inline-block;padding:12px 28px;background:#4285f4;color:#fff;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:15px'>🔐 Sign in with Google</a></div>",
        "formFields": { "values": [] },
        "options": {
          "formTitle": "Authentication Error",
          "buttonLabel": "← Retry Sign-In"
        }
      },
      "id": "bb000004-bbbb-4bbb-8bbb-bbbbbbbbbb04",
      "name": "Form — Auth Error",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.form",
